{"tid":2426684,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"無綫今晚直播一小時悼念特輯 追憶達叔","createTime":"2021-02-28T09:15:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T10:30:27.000Z","uid":25345,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"75c318fc7794555b65973116ad498e4cb427fe26","tid":2426684,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T09:15:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20210228/s00009/0748c03ac0b5d379512fcb801f17e92d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20210228%2Fs00009%2F0748c03ac0b5d379512fcb801f17e92d.jpg&h=d0646fac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n吳孟達（達哥）昨天（27日）因肝癌病逝。達哥年輕時因投考無綫電視藝員訓練班而入行，從影40多年來拍過無數劇集和電影，1991年更憑電影《天若有情》奪香港電影金像獎最佳男配角，是公認的實力派演員。<br />\n<br />\n無綫今晚9時半至10時半直播一小時悼念特輯《無可比擬的演藝泰斗 永遠懷念吳孟達》，邀請羅冠蘭、麥鎮江、伍潤泉、甄懋強、吳麗珠 、鄧英敏、商天娥、戴志偉、關禮傑、王晶、苑瓊丹、林子聰等圈中好友現身，分享達哥生前的點滴。節目主持則包括汪明荃、鄧梓峰、黎芷珊、陳貝兒及陸浩明 。"},{"pid":"0ef6b48b41883156df221629398b50f33ea566f0","tid":2426684,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T09:19:40.000Z","msg":"會唔會變數臭周星馳大會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b107ff80d8ceeee3320c04d48ae661c86eb1f66","tid":2426684,"uid":80548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T09:32:23.000Z","msg":"即刻開返首Funkytown黎聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb720facd07dae66b3c4c42a6d4845a38ae439ee","tid":2426684,"uid":23468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ef6b48b41883156df221629398b50f33ea566f0","tid":2426684,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T09:19:40.000Z","msg":"會唔會變數臭周星馳大會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T09:37:02.000Z","msg":"點會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ntvb到時仲要攪周星星悼念大會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f77b696cb7d3f20e26a677d0f3d4b8a